channel.description:
![](upload://gZgBYvztK4mG4LDmvBLMvQRaZlS.jpeg)
![](upload://v4lT8k4qTwchfxDeCQhCoeGvUaN.jpeg)
I know everyone wanted updates so here's my thread! Finally started building this behemoth on Monday night, got through quite a lot of it after a few hours of building. I was playing Gears 3 last night so no building, but I'll get back on it tonight.
[url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fbs76l6FGqo]LEGO Super Star Destroyer 10221 - Build update[/url] | Everyone was asleep so the video is silent.
[url='https://jambo.imgur.com/S2F1M#qoTuX']Build gallery[/url]

The technic stuff was incredibly time consuming, but it's made the thing damn sturdy!

item.title: jambo's LEGO thread of Super Star Destroyers
item.dc:creator: Bolteh
item.description:
This is the kind of Lego that rocks, the kind where you have the classic blocks with only a few unique shapes thrown into them.

Lego had this dark period not long ago where nearly the entire thing was prefab and you just had to click 4-5 parts together and add a few random classic blocks for lulz.

Kind of sad that I don’t have the room to display these kinds of awesome builds. Who knows, maybe one day.
